      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her\u2014she\u2019s basically in showroom condition with not a single scratch or dent in sight! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that amazing 'new car' feel inside and out. I'm really sad to see it go, but I'm looking for a great new home for it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
