    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine, collector-quality condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings, Vanos system, and rear subframe\u2014the 'Big Three' for this chassis\u2014have been meticulously addressed with documented precision. The factory M-Variable limited-slip differential provides exceptional longitudinal traction, while the suspension retains its original damping characteristics and bushing compliance for a sharp, communicative turn-in. With flawless original paint and a cockpit free of bolster wear, this M3 offers the tactile, analog driving experience that defines the era.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
