      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is an absolute time capsule; the exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, the original carpets are protected by pristine mats, and it has never been smoked in. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the heated seats, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by certified technicians with a full, documented service history included in a comprehensive binder. The engine bay is detailed and dry, the transmission shifts are imperceptible, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Serious inquiries only for this investment-quality vehicle.",
